<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Nicheng In Ka en !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka lopina ding leh ka bitna mun,
 Gal lauhum leh kihchak um lohna;
 Gamgaw apat hin ginna'n ka vak mui,
 Kumsawt gam chun ei tuom vel ahi.

[V2]
 Ni chengin en ka, ka tun masang cheng,
 A hehpihna nun khawnuom gam chu;
 Mite'n zie mun chu lui di'n gingchau ui,
 Ka gen thei puoi, thakin a kilang.

[V3]
 2. Zie phat tieng chu leh namtin chitin ten,
 A lopina vak zam vel a chun;
 Hukdam haw mel vak hawih leh lopi chu,
 A muh tieng uleh gingcha tan au.

[V4]
 3. Chun, dantak leh A cha hehpih haw chu,
 Kumsawt Zingsawl Aksi vakhawih chu;
 Kei a ahung hiu umsahaw cheng tawh,
 Kumsawt nawpla chu sakhawm taitiu.

[V5]
 4. Ka thagau lungkham leh vakvai kawmah,
 Krista'n A hehpihna thu hing chu;
 A na hetsak phal tak mai ziek chun Aw,
 Hallelujah chawian chim puong ie.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>135</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
</song>